  "text": "The flow supported by our framework is based on the \"Visual Information Seeking Mantra\" formalized by Shneiderman [CITATION_1] . It consists of supporting a sequential flow of actions: first getting an overview and then zooming and filtering with details on demand. This mantra is a recognized way to design advanced graphical user interfaces.",
